Description :
More than 80 years ago the legendary Florentine, the priceless imperial diamond of the Austrian emperors, was lost in the Caribbean with the sinking of the Pride. The courageous treasure hunter Annie O'Connors is on a mission to recover the prized gem in this exciting Hidden Object game. Can you help her? Accompany Annie on her exciting treasure hunt and uncover the Curse of the Ghost Ship.

